Checks: '-*,bugprone-*,performance-*,readability-*,modernize-*,clang-analyzer-*,-modernize-use-trailing-return-type'
WarningsAsErrors: '*'
HeaderFilterRegex: 'src/|include/'
FormatStyle: none
AnalyzeTemporaryDtors: false
## Policy Note (DR-0003): Core performance modules must remain exception free.
